Steps.Message: Update at 15:37 - Our engineers have completed their investigations and have found damage to our substation equipment. They have also become aware that further power has been lost in the area. They will shortly be able to restore supplies to approximately half the properties currently affected, by redirecting more power around the damaged section of our network. More customers will be be back on by reconfiguring the network, with the final properties being restored by the temporary generators. As a result, power will come back on in the area in stages, with the final properties being restored between 18:30 and 19:30. We're sorry this is taking longer than expected, and we'll continue to keep you up to date. Thanks for bearing with us.

We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
